传奇R＆B歌手和芝加哥政治家杰里·巴特勒（Jerry Butler）死于85岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-rb-singer-ander-and--chicago------------------ jerry-butler-dies-dies-85-3840392?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = legendary-rb-singer-singer and-chicago-pilitician-pilitician-jerry-jerry-butler-dies-85Laura Molloy Sat, 22 Feb 2025 10:00:56 +0000 Music NewsNews..R&BSoul https://www.nme.com/?p=3840392 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手被称为“冰人”，与柯蒂斯·梅菲尔德（Curtis Mayfield）建立了持久的创造性关系</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-rb-singer-and-chicago-politician-jerry-butler-dies-aged-85-3840392">传奇的R＆B歌手和芝加哥政治家杰里·巴特勒（Jerry Butler）死于85岁，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jerry-Butler-in-1980.-CREDIT_-Paul-Natkin_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>灵魂歌手和伊利诺伊州政客杰里·巴特勒（Jerry Butler）去世，享年85岁。</p><p>一位家人朋友向<a href="https://chicago.suntimes.com/obituaries/2025/02/21/jerry-butler-iceman-impressions-curtis-mayfield-rock-roll-hall-fame-cook-county-board" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>芝加哥太阳时代</em></a>证实，巴特勒于周四（2月20日）在他的芝加哥家去世。没有死亡原因，但他一直在帕金森氏病。</p><p>巴特勒（Butler）出生于密西西比州，在芝加哥长大，最初受过训练为厨师，但最终在1950年代中期与柯蒂斯·梅菲尔德（Curtis Mayfield）见面后，最终为印象的早期迭代做出了贡献。</p><p>他与小组一起演出了三年，并最终写下了1958年的热门单曲《为您的宝贵爱》，当年在美国排名第11位。然后，他离开了独自职业，梅菲尔德开始领导该小组。</p><p>巴特勒（Butler）与梅菲尔德（Mayfield）继续写作，两人巴特勒（Butler）的1960年热门歌曲“他会伤心了”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/otis-redding">奥蒂斯·雷丁（Otis Redding&#39;S&#39;S&#39;S”（Otis Redding</a> ）&#39;我一直爱你太久了”  - 后者将是后者由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aretha-franklin">Aretha Franklin</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/etta-james">Etta James</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jason-isbell">Jason Isbell</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cat-power">Cat Power</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">Rolling Stones</a>覆盖。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="他会伤你的心" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Qbt5fBBelrs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>巴特勒后来与费城灵魂词曲作者肯尼·赌博和莱昂·霍夫（Leon Huff）合作，为他的1962年经典专辑《 The Ice Man Cometh》（The Ice Man Cometh）伪造了道路，其中以热门单曲为“ Only the Strong Surrive&#39;&#39;，而“永不放弃您”。</p><p>在70年代，巴特勒（Butler）于1994年开始了他家乡伊利诺伊州的库克县董事会专员。</p><p>他对音乐的贡献得到了广泛的认可：1991年，他因印象而入选摇滚名人堂，并在2015年进入全国节奏和蓝调名人堂作为独奏艺术家，然后他们终身荣幸地为他致敬。 2023年成就奖。</p><p>根据芝加哥<em>太阳时代</em>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/smokey-robinson">烟熏罗宾逊</a>向巴特勒致敬，称他为“我们那个时代的最大声音之一”，并补充说：“他是一个伟大的人，我爱他。”</p><p>肯尼·甘布尔（Kenny Gamble）和莱昂·霍夫（Leon Huff）在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/jerry-butler-impressions-singer-chicago-politician-dead-obituary-1235274963/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>引用的联合声明中说：“我们深切而真诚地为失去了亲爱的和长期的朋友杰里·巴特勒（Jerry Butler Aka）又名《冰人》（The Iceman）的失落，以表彰他的凉爽，流畅的人声和举止。他是一种音乐传奇人物！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-rb-singer-and-chicago-politician-jerry-butler-dies-aged-85-3840392">传奇的R＆B歌手和芝加哥政治家杰里·巴特勒（Jerry Butler）死于85岁，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
